{"tid":2157596,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"買《蘋果》過機變另一報章「篤數」？7-11：店員誤掃條碼 絕不影響對數","createTime":"2020-08-15T06:42:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T10:49:11.000Z","uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"751a43d2694e48a10c894cd5baa65af9e70aa3c5","tid":2157596,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:42:45.000Z","msg":"有多名網民發現，在7-11便利店購買《蘋果日報》時，收銀時被錯誤輸入為另一份報章，惹來買《蘋果日報》卻變為另一報章「篤數」的疑雲。<br />\n<br />\n網民公開的單據顯示，他購買《蘋果日報》但單據上卻顯示為《東方日報》，需要向收銀員提示後始改為《蘋果日報》。不少留言亦表示有同一情況，擔心支持《蘋果日報》會變相「被支持」另一報章，亦影響《蘋果》收入。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因應網民關注，《蘋果》發行部向7-11查問有關事宜，獲回覆稱事件是源於店員為方便客戶買報紙時的運作，會用一塊集合所有報紙條碼（BARCODE）的紙板過機；而就有關情況，7-11方面已向該店舖了解，當時客戶購買《蘋果日報》時，店員可能誤掃《東方日報》的條碼，已即時通知店員要小心留意。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/I6EVDLCJ55CXVGJH7AFOFBJOSY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FI6EVDLCJ55CXVGJH7AFOFBJOSY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8frdRd5YSNtYq48oyOX%2FX2w%3D&h=12cca1f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FI6EVDLCJ55CXVGJH7AFOFBJOSY%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=3ae81e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/I6EVDLCJ55CXVGJH7AFOFBJOSY/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"b18a3446768cfcd965281af6b4dbf88b7355362a","tid":2157596,"uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:44:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21106363f93c0371e2b2302e2ddf39928bd7df75","tid":2157596,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"sco